        <initializer>	800000 1175000 1207000 1217000 1221000 1226000 1233000 1245000 1266000 1299000 1366000</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Default open-circuit voltage curve for nickel-cadmium (NiCd) batteries. </para>
